<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">

    <title>비밀번호 찾기</title>
    <%- include('header.ejs') %>

</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-primary">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Outer Row -->
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-xl-10 col-lg-12 col-md-9">
                <div class="card o-hidden border-0 shadow-lg my-5">
                    <div class="card-body p-0">
                        <!-- Nested Row within Card Body -->
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-6 d-none d-lg-block bg-password-image"></div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="p-5">
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <h6 class="h4 text-gray-900 mb-2">비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?</h6>
                                        <br>
                                        <div class="text-primary">
                                        <i class="small" >
                                            전화번호를 입력 해 주세요. 
                                            <br>문자인증 후  비밀번호를 수정할 수 있습니다.
                                        </i>
                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <form class="user" action="/auth" method="post">
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-user"
                                                id="_phone" name="phone"
                                                placeholder="Enter Phone Number...">
                                                <br>
                                            <div class="text-center">    
                                                <!-- <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="location.href='/auth'">문자인증</button> -->
                                                <button class="btn btn-primary" >인증호전송</button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                        
                                    <form class="user" action="/verify" method="post">
                                        <br>
                                        <div class="text-success">
                                            <label class="small">※ 잠시 후 인중번호가 휴대폰으로 <br>전송됩니다.(4자리 이하) </label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-user"
                                            id="auth_code" name='input_auth_code'  placeholder="Enter SMS Verification text..">
                                        </div>
                                        <br>
                                        <br>
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <div class="text-center">
                                                <button class="btn btn-primary" >문자인증</button>
                                            </div> 
                                        </div>
                                    </form>  
                                    <hr>
                                        
                                        <!-- <a href="my.ejs" class="btn btn-primary btn-user btn-block"> -->
                                           <!-- 비밀번호를 재설정 하세요 -->
                                        <!-- </a> -->
                                    <!-- </form> -->
                                    <hr>
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <a class="small" href="/signup">회원가입</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <a class="small" href="/">이미 회원 가입하셨다면 로그인</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>